  <wpt lat="41.265233" lon="-96.039317">
    <time>2026-07-20T11:00:00</time>
    <name>GCBRHHB</name>
    <desc>Omaha Lunch #85 by Monty12, Event Cache (1.0/1.5)</desc>
    <url>https://coord.info/GCBRHHB</url>
    <urlname>Omaha Lunch #85</urlname>
    <sym>Geocache</sym>
    <type>Geocache|Event Cache</type>
    <groundspeak:cache id="10479470" archived="False" available="True" xmlns:groundspeak="http://www.groundspeak.com/cache/1/0/1">
      <groundspeak:name>Omaha Lunch #85</groundspeak:name>
      <groundspeak:placed_by>Monty12</groundspeak:placed_by>
      <groundspeak:owner id="1253738">Monty12</groundspeak:owner>
      <groundspeak:type>Event Cache</groundspeak:type>
      <groundspeak:container>Other</groundspeak:container>
      <groundspeak:attributes />
      <groundspeak:difficulty>1.0</groundspeak:difficulty>
      <groundspeak:terrain>1.5</groundspeak:terrain>
      <groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country>
      <groundspeak:state>Nebraska</groundspeak:state>
      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;20 July 2026, 11:00 - 12:15&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;Welcome to this monthly geocaching event series, which will hopefully take you to different locations each month for lunch in the greater Omaha area. Here is the info for July 2026:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When:&lt;/strong&gt; Monday, July 20th, 2026 (11:00am - 12:15pm)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;Culver&amp;#39;s     11920 Miami St.   Omaha, NE&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What:&lt;/strong&gt; I picked this Culver&amp;#39;s because it is centrally located in the greater Omaha metropolitan area.  So, no more excuses of long drives.  &lt;img alt="smiley" height="23" src="https://cdn.ckeditor.com/4.22.1/full-all/plugins/smiley/images/regular_smile.png" title="smiley" width="23" /&gt; Depending on the weather (and crowds) we will meet outside at the tables or inside in the corner area.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As always, no purchase is necessary. Just come by to visit and have a good time.  &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Event ownership is open to everyone, and the event owner decides on the date, time, and location, preferably someplace new to the event (see the long list of places already used). If you would like to be the event owner for next month, please attend this current event or coordinate with the current event owner before the next event.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This monthly lunch has been going on since January 23, 2017... pretty impressive!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Past Omaha Lunch Events&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #001 at Don &amp;amp; Millies hosted by TeamDAAK&lt;br /&gt;
