      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:&amp;amp;quot;"&gt;Drinks and socializing with geocaching friends.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:&amp;amp;quot;"&gt;Come to Speilbound for drinks and socializing after a long day of geocaching.  The coffee shop is Spielbound.  No purchase is necessary.  All you need to do is show up and “hi.”  The street address is 3229 Harney St., Omaha, NE 68131.  There is on-street parking on Harney and a parking garage across Harney from the coffee shop.  See you there.  Time will be from 5:00 pm to 6:00 pm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional Waypoints&lt;/p&gt;P0BRN63 - Parking&lt;br /&gt;N 41° 15.408 W 095° 57.650&lt;br /&gt;Parking garage.  First 2 hours are free.&lt;br /&gt;</groundspeak:long_description>
