  <wpt lat="42.76455" lon="-98.055167">
    <time>2026-06-27T11:15:00</time>
    <name>GCBKV7N</name>
    <desc>Event With a View - 2026 by Niobrara State Park, Event Cache (1.0/1.0)</desc>
    <url>https://coord.info/GCBKV7N</url>
    <urlname>Event With a View - 2026</urlname>
    <sym>Geocache</sym>
    <type>Geocache|Event Cache</type>
    <groundspeak:cache id="10338864" archived="False" available="True" xmlns:groundspeak="http://www.groundspeak.com/cache/1/0/1">
      <groundspeak:name>Event With a View - 2026</groundspeak:name>
      <groundspeak:placed_by>Niobrara State Park</groundspeak:placed_by>
      <groundspeak:owner id="9631483">Niobrara State Park</groundspeak:owner>
      <groundspeak:type>Event Cache</groundspeak:type>
      <groundspeak:container>Other</groundspeak:container>
      <groundspeak:attributes>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="24" inc="1">Wheelchair accessible</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="8" inc="1">Scenic view</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="25" inc="1">Parking nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="2" inc="1">Access/parking fee</groundspeak:attribute>
      </groundspeak:attributes>
      <groundspeak:difficulty>1.0</groundspeak:difficulty>
      <groundspeak:terrain>1.0</groundspeak:terrain>
      <groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country>
      <groundspeak:state>Nebraska</groundspeak:state>
      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;27 June 2026, 11:15 - 13:30&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;June 27 2026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11:15 - 13:30&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Come and make this years annual &amp;quot;Event With a Veiw 2026 something special!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This event will take place at Niobrara State Park. The gathering before the event will begin on Friday, June 26th and continue with the event at noon on Saturday the 27th from 11:15 am till 1:30 pm. There may be other non event gatherings through Sunday June 28th at Niobrara State Park near Niobrara Ne.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The fun will start on Friday evening June 26th at 7:00PM with a campfire and s&amp;#39;mores gathering by our camper. (watch for our sign).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;big&gt;&lt;img src="http://imgcdn.geocaching.com/cache/large/04ce4cc4-5518-4421-a751-39f8975f51a9.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/big&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This year&amp;#39;s &amp;quot;Event With a View&amp;quot; is going to be held on June 27th, from 11:15 AM until 1:30 PM, at the Buffalo Cookout Pavilion located in Niobrara State Park. There will also be non-event activities other than the main event during the weekend.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An annual or daily Nebraska Park Entry Permit is required to enter the park.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Preregistration and announcements will begin at 9:00 AM at the Buffalo Cookout Pavilion. Don&amp;#39;t forget to bring your bug spray and sunscreen. This scenic, tranquil park offers cabins, both primitive and RV camping, picnicking, swimming, horseback trails, hiking, fishing and wildlife watching opportunities. If hiking is your style, there are over 14 miles of hiking trails in the Park. There are also a variety of caches throughout the park, as well as in the surrounding area for attendees that would like to go geocaching before or after the event. If you so desire, a file of geocaches will be available for download. Please bring any cables your device needs for this to occur. You may hang around the shelter if that is your pleasure but if you choose to leave for whatever reason please return to the shelter between 11:30 and 1:30 for lunch, conversation and the Event. Sandwiches will be provided.  Please bring a side dish to share.  Prize drawing will be at 12:30 p.m. It should make an enjoyable day for everyone!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Camping is available in the park. Call 402-857-3373 to check availability.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cell phone coverage may be limited depending on your carrier.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Watch this cache page for further announcements, and other activities that will be happening in the park over the weekend.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are sure to be new caches released in the park on the event date. If you want to hunt geocaches during your stay at the park bring your GPS Saturday morning to the Buffalo Cookout Pavilion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please indicate your desire to attend by logging a &amp;quot;Will Attend&amp;quot; entry.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A special THANK YOU to the Niobrara State Park management for allowing and welcoming Geocaching in this GREAT park.&lt;/p&gt;
</groundspeak:long_description>
      <groundspeak:encoded_hints>
      </groundspeak:encoded_hints>
      <groundspeak:logs>
