      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;08 June 2026, 11:30 - 12:30&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;Welcome to this monthly geocaching event series, which will hopefully take you to different locations each month for lunch in the greater Omaha area. Here is the info for June 2026:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;When:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Monday, June 8, 2026 (11:30am - 12:30pm)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;Where:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt; &lt;em&gt;Williamsburg Pizza&lt;/em&gt; at 15526 Spaulding Plaza (just North of 156&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; and Maple)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;What:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt; Pizza of course! During lunch, they offer four different pizza slice combo meals that can be prepared quickly. If that&amp;rsquo;s not your thing they have a full menu of whole pizzas, pasta, salads, sides and desserts!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;As always, no purchase is necessary. Just come by to visit and have a good time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;Event ownership is open to everyone, and the event owner decides on the date, time, and location, preferably someplace new to the event (see the long list of places already used). If you would like to be the event owner for next month, please attend this current event or coordinate with the current event owner before the next event.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Comic Sans MS,cursive"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:12pt"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11.0pt"&gt;This monthly lunch has been going on since January 23, 2017... pretty impressive!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:11px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Past Omaha Lunch Events&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;
